<p>Brooke shrugged. </p>
<p>"I've never been attracted to another woman before. Hell, I've never felt like this about anyone ever, male or female. I just love her". </p>
<p>Nicole rolled her eyes and pretended to gag. Brooke glared at her.  </p>
